CX4 coprocessor: point the Data ROM init at the vendored path
(rtl/upstream/chip/CX4/drom.mif) and add save state support (SS register
window, RAMIO $6000 Data RAM access, idle gating). CX4 SS ported from
SNES_MiSTer PR #487.

